    "Extended Summary": {
      "children": [
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The "
            },
            {
              "type": "inlineCode",
              "value": "FacetGrid"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " is an object that links a xarray DataArray to a Matplotlib figure with a particular structure."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "In particular, "
            },
            {
              "type": "inlineCode",
              "value": "FacetGrid"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " is used to draw plots with multiple axes, where each axes shows the same relationship conditioned on different levels of some dimension. It's possible to condition on up to two variables by assigning variables to the rows and columns of the grid."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The general approach to plotting here is called \"small multiples\", where the same kind of plot is repeated multiple times, and the specific use of small multiples to display the same relationship conditioned on one ore more other variables is often called a \"trellis plot\"."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "The basic workflow is to initialize the "
            },
            {
              "type": "inlineCode",
              "value": "FacetGrid"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " object with the DataArray and the variable names that are used to structure the grid. Then plotting functions can be applied to each subset by calling "
            },
            {
              "type": "inlineCode",
              "value": "FacetGrid.map_dataarray"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": " or "
            },
            {
              "type": "inlineCode",
              "value": "FacetGrid.map"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "level": 0,
      "target": null,
